2014-05-07  1.0-4  Algorithms improved:
                   - An incorrect (and, fortunately, almost never used) branch
                     removed from binom.blaker.lower.limit.R.
                   - Maximum number of interval halving steps newly controlled
                     by a parameter. (Infinite loops resulting from too small
                     numerical tolerance parameter values thus avoided.)
                   - Input parameter checks added.
                   - Unnecessary calculations of binomial quantiles eliminated.  

